OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAn overcast start with periods
OL,6,Fof rain, heavy at times and combining
OL,7,Fwith gales to bring decidedly un-
OL,8,FSpring like weather. Clearing to
OL,9,Fblustery showers during the morning,
OL,10,Fwith these heavy for the afternoon and
OL,11,Fturning wintry across higher ground.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FBlustery showers pushing
OL,14,Facross the area on strong to gale west
OL,15,Fto southwest winds. Outbreaks frequent
OL,16,Fand heavy in west, occasional in east
OL,17,Fand turning wintry to quite low levels.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,176,160,301,260,100,100
