OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FShowers continuing, frequent
OL,6,Fin the west, occasional in east, but
OL,7,Foutbreaks lighter than Thursday night
OL,8,Fwith sleet and snow increasingly
OL,9,Fconfined to higher areas. Limited
OL,10,Fbrighter spells best towards Inverness.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FShowers
OL,13,Ffor Saturday focused in west, with
OL,14,FInverness best sheltered. Rain early
OL,15,FSunday, clearing to blustery showers
OL,16,Fby afternoon, wintry across hills.
OL,17,FScattered showers then periods of rain
OL,18,Ffor Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
